### Overall Grade: **B+**

Strong week execution (+2.27% vs SPY -0.13% est = +2.40% alpha). Phase alpha still negative (-1.46%) from early SPY gap — closing the deficit. No rule violations. Risk management held on volatile days. One drag (XOM energy headwinds) preventing A grade; capital under-deployment also a concern. Execution quality high.
